$ Excel: Insert -> Links

Create *hyperlinks* to files, webpages, places in this document, to create new documents and eMail addresses

sa:
  The → Microsoft/Office/Excel/functions/hyperlink[`hyperlink()`] → Microsoft/Office/Excel/functions[worksheet function]

  The → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Hyperlink[`hyperlink`] object.

  The → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Worksheet event → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Hyperlink/followHyperlink[`followHyperlink`].
